    "course_title": "TRANSFORMATIVE NURSING CAPSTONE",
    "description": "Integration of learning acquired throughout the nursing program. Learning outcomes integrate concepts associated with five nursing program meta concepts (professionalism; person, family, community, and systems-centered care; health and illness; health care context; and scholarship for evidence-based practice). Using processes of analysis, synthesis, reflection, and application, advance in your transition to becoming a professional nurse. Includes mentoring through co- facilitation by faculty, academic staff, and practice professionals.",
